WEBVTT

00:00:04.220 --> 00:00:05.760
What's right for you

00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:08.420
doesn't necessarily work for the next person.

00:00:10.760 --> 00:00:14.740
Customization isn't always just the question of preference though

00:00:14.740 --> 00:00:16.600
Sometimes it's a necessity.

00:00:21.380 --> 00:00:26.000
Being able to adjust the text is crucial for people with low vision and dyslexia.

00:00:34.660 --> 00:00:39.000
Properly coded websites and applications allow the text to be customized.

00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:43.560
For example, to change its size, spacing, font, and colors

00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:45.800
without loss of functions or clarity.

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:04.400
Web accessibility: Essential for some, useful for all.